  "version": "0.13.0",
  "description": "Built-in background-removal utility with unified BiRefNet/rembg/SAM engine resolution, portable RMBG capability inventory and safety gates, multi-subject Interactive SAM, prompt-based Segmentation Lab, face/clothes/fashion region segmentation, RMBG mask/object utilities, live-gated Mask Overlay, Lama object removal, Image + Mask Resize, Image Crop preparation, model-aware advanced matting, live-gated Flux Kontext context-latent assist, bounded image batches, and frame-wise video segmentation.",
