      "notes": [
        "Smart mode prefers the installed Comfy BiRefNet route for general, portrait, product, fine-edge, and low-VRAM presets.",
        "Anime prefers the optional native rembg ISNet Anime route when that runtime is installed.",
        "Fallback never guesses missing assets: exact Comfy models come from the live catalog and native models come from rembg-supported model IDs.",
        "Mask Review remains a Comfy-only non-destructive refinement route and never reruns segmentation.",
        "Interactive Select can keep multiple independently selected subjects. Box-only selections prefer the exact Impact Pack SAMLoader/SAMDetectorCombined route and reuse ADetailer models from ComfyUI/models/sams; point corrections use Native ONNX SAM.",
        "Comfy SAM loads one .pth checkpoint per workflow, creates one mask per selected subject, unions only selected masks, and can hand the combined gate to an installed Comfy BiRefNet model for soft-edge refinement."
      ]
    },
